lead_paragraph: Tammy Williams and Garland Cooper hit back-to-back homers in the eighth inning as Northwestern ousted top-seeded U.C.L.A., 3-1, in the Women's College World Series in Oklahoma City. In a best-of-three championship series beginning today, Northwestern will face Arizona.
